  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lumina Rush – Speed, Style, and Competition!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ <strong>Slide, blast, and swing</strong> your way through adrenaline-pumping levels in <strong>Lumina Rush</strong>, the ultimate momentum-based platformer! Master every movement, <strong>shave off seconds</strong>, and dominate the leaderboards. Got the reflexes? Prove it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feel the Speed</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level is designed to let you <strong>keep up the momentum</strong>—find the fastest route, execute the perfect moves, and push your skills to the limit. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn medals, discover collectibles, and unlock <strong>stylish cosmetics</strong> to make your character stand out as you race to victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create & Compete</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own <strong>custom levels</strong> with the <strong>intuitive level editor</strong>, share them with the world, and challenge others to beat your best times on the leaderboards!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Race Your Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on your rivals in <strong>head-to-head versus mode</strong>—who’s got the fastest reflexes and the sharpest routes? There's only one way to find out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Strap in, rev up, and experience the rush!</strong> 🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lumina Rush – Speed, Style, and Competition!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ <strong>Slide, blast, and swing</strong> your way through adrenaline-pumping levels in <strong>Lumina Rush</strong>, the ultimate momentum-based platformer! Master every movement, <strong>shave off seconds</strong>, and dominate the leaderboards. Got the reflexes? Prove it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feel the Speed</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/5fc6f4f5bf09aea47fd4164978f43cdd.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level is designed to let you <strong>keep up the momentum</strong>—find the fastest route, execute the perfect moves, and push your skills to the limit. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/9e4f128133aed13aedceeddcc89d4fc5.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn medals, discover collectibles, and unlock <strong>stylish cosmetics</strong> to make your character stand out as you race to victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create & Compete</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/ce17c0f1a469f280f28751cfe5b5b813.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own <strong>custom levels</strong> with the <strong>intuitive level editor</strong>, share them with the world, and challenge others to beat your best times on the leaderboards!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Race Your Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.poster.avif?t=1741038512\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.webm?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872830/extras/8cb31895c4c7f4381633e37562608156.mp4?t=1741038512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on your rivals in <strong>head-to-head versus mode</strong>—who’s got the fastest reflexes and the sharpest routes? There's only one way to find out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Strap in, rev up, and experience the rush!</strong> 🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
